p.d: Winter Games New Zealand is an annual elite international winter sports event, attracting the world’s best athletes. This will be the seventh edition of the Games, taking place during August and September 2019 in Queenstown, Wanaka and Naseby. The Winter Games NZ is the premier winter sports event in the Southern Hemisphere and one of the top 5 in the world, with 26 snow and events at 6 venues over 17 action packed days.
